metadata.name: To Kill a Fixed Identity
metadata.description:
To Kill a Fixed Identity is a live theatrical performance artwork performed by Samuel van Keeken in Amsterdam, February 2022. 

The TKFI NFT set is a collection of digital collectable performance art. The owner of this NFT will be allowed to come and see all future live performances made by me. 

For this I need to be able to contact you, so please feel free to get in touch with me at www.samuelvankeeken.com
